Welcome to TCQ
About Us
At The Cigar Quarters, LLC our clientâs best interest come first, and everything we do will be guided by our values and professional ethics. We will ensure that we hold ourselves accountable to the highest standards by delivering excellent entertainment and needed jobs to the area.
We cultivate a working environment that provides a human, sustainable approach to earning a living, and living in our world, for our partners, employees and for our clients.
Our Mission
Our mission is to establish a Cigar Lounge business that will make available:
wide range of premium Cigars, alcoholic
non â alcoholic wines
beers from top brands at affordable prices with a surreal ambiance
networking environment
safe cigar storage lockers
huge walk-in humidor
smooth jazz
live band experience
to the residence and visitors of Polk County - Florida
OUR VISION
The Cigar Quarters, LLC is a neighborhood High Class Cigar Lounge that is located in an easily accessible, centralized area between a residential neighborhood and a busy business district in downtown Haines City - Florida.
PARTNERS
The Cigar Quarters is a partnership business that is owned and operated by Grant Enterprises USA (GEU). The business is managed by Anthony C. Grant Sr., T. Cheuhai Grant, Bernard Stephens and Larry T. Grant Jr. 
The group has experience and success in several lines of business. They bring their experience and expertise to help build and grow The Cigar  Quarters to compete favorably with other leading cigar lounges.
